Applying SVM¶

In [52]:
x=train.iloc[:,0:13]
x.shape
Out[52]:
(30161, 13)
In [51]:
y=train.iloc[:,13]
y.shape
Out[51]:
(30161,)
In [53]:
model_svm = SVC()
In [54]:
clf = model_svm.fit(x,y)
pred = clf.predict(x)
In [67]:
train['Pred_Salary']=pred
